column2: select a.eid,Age_at_recruitment_#,Sex_#,Ethnic_background_#,        Age_started_wearing_glasses_or_contact_lenses_#,Qualifications_#,        Reason_for_glasses_contact_lenses_#,Height_#,Weight_#,Body_mass_index_BMI__#,        Ever_had_refractive_laser_eye_surgery_#  from dbo.Baseline_characteristics b inner join dbo.Eye_surgery_complications a       cross apply openjson(Ever_had_refractive_laser_eye_surgery_#) j on a.eid=b.eid  inner join dbo.Ethnicity e on a.eid=e.eid inner join dbo.Eyesight y on a.eid=y.eid inner join dbo.Body_size_measures o on a.eid=o.eid inner join dbo.Education d on a.eid=d.eid where j.value in (#,#,#)
